

Intall Node.js

Verify the node version and npm version with 'node -v' 'npm -v'

Use 'npm install --save -dev cypress' to install latest version

Use 'npx cypress open' to configure and install cypress

To excecute the scripts use 'npm run cypress:open' with headed mode and test runner

To execute the scripts use 'npm run cypress:run' with headless mode


